<author>wlym jndy, wlym jndy</author>
<title>qd fdạny bạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (qd fdạny bạlṣlyb .. qd hdạny dẖạ ạlḥbyb
 rạfʿaⁿạ ḥmly ạltẖqyl .. dẖạ ḥbyby yạ jmwʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹sạ̉lwny ʿn yswʿ .. ḥbh byn ạlḍlwʿ)2
 (dẖạ nṣyby̱ dẖạ fdạỷy .. dẖạ ḥbyby yạ jmwʿ)2
 2- (km sẖfạny mn sqạm .. km jlạ ʿny ạlẓlạm
 km ạ̉ḥạṭt by ydạh .. dẖạ ḥbyby yạ jmwʿ)2
 3- (dẖạ ʿzạʾuⁿ ly ydwm .. wsṭ ạ̉gẖmạr ạlhmwm
 qd ʿrft ḥbh .. dẖạ ḥbyby yạ jmwʿ)2
 4- (fy ạlṭryq ly rfyq .. fy ạlmsyr ly ṣdyq
 ybqy̱ kẖly fy ạlḥyạẗ .. dẖạ ḥbyby yạ jmwʿ)2</lyrics>
</song>